707448f-a.text:
165 Woodruff Ave.. Inorth side, between Ocean and Flatbush Aves. The

1931.

707449f-a.title: Brooklyn: Woodruff Ave. - Ocean Ave.
707449f-a.text:
Woodruff Ave., north side, between Ocean and Flatbush Aves.1 also
Ocean Ave., between Parkside and Woodruff Aves. The frame house on the
corner was razed in 1927, to make way for a 6-story building.
April 1927.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
